ative pressures; or alternatively, we verify\nthat repulsive gravity may occur for standard matter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Jul 2014 23:19:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 May 2015 11:13:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-08"}
