ts show this\nvelocity bias introduces another systematic, alongside scale-dependent halo\nmass bias, which cannot be neglected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jul 2014 00:28:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
