s are able to connect most spiral tracers. A\nmodel of polynomial-logarithmic spirals is also proposed, which not only\ndelineates the tracer distribution, but also matches the observed tangential\ndirections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jul 2014 06:22:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Sep 2014 01:12:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Oct 2014 08:48:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-15"}
